text: {'text': 'Well this is our home church so obviously I love it. But subjective comments aside, the church serves multiple ethnicities / languages: English, Chinese, Indonesian, even Myanmar. No fewer than 6 regular weekly services on Sundays, each 30 minutes apart. So please do come, worship and be blessed... whether you are long-time believers, recent Christians, or want to know more about salvation through Jesus Christ.', 'languageCode': 'en'}
